'''William Henry Heaton''' (26 August 1918 – 16 January 1990) was an English footballer who played in [[the Football League]] for [[Leeds United F.C.|Leeds United]], [[Southampton F.C.|Southampton]] and [[Rochdale A.F.C.|Rochdale]].

